$Id: README,v 1.1 2007/09/25 11:53:44 rjones Exp $

Nagios (http://www.nagios.org/) is a system monitoring package.

Nagios-virt is a tool for configuring Nagios so that it can monitor
guests on a Xen-, QEMU- or KVM-based host.  It takes care of setting
up the complicated configuration files for you.
